 } } \right| = 0$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow 3(1 - y + 2 - z) - 2( - x + 2 + z - 2) = 0$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow 9 - 3y - 3z + 2x - 2z = 0$$<br><br>$$ \Rightarrow 2x - 3y - 5z + 9 = 0$$<br><br>By checking all options you can see ($$-$$2, 0, 1) satisfy the equation.
